Revision history for Perl distribution Win32-Mechanize-NotepadPlusPlus

v0.002003 (internal:2020-Apr-04)
    - look into why messages were missing, and add them (#29)
    - TODO: add historical notes, to say that that the methods from this list (below)
        requires NPP v7.8 (because these are the SCI v4.2.0 updates);
        probably also need a note or check somewhere that it requires NPP v7.7 for many of the messages
        (and no backward compatibility is guaranteed)

    - Notepad_plus_msgs.h:
        fix comment on line 381(379) to match message; no new messages
    - menuCmdID.h:
        525: add IDM_LANG_OPENUDLDIR
        533: rename IDM_ONLINEHELP => IDM_ONLINEDOCUMENT
    - scintilla.h:
